                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Store LLM API keys in Vault with KV versioning; use ExternalSecret Operator to sync into Kubernetes without embedding keys in pod specs."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Rotate on a fixed schedule (30 days is common) via an automated pipeline \u2014 provision, validate, swap Vault, wait grace window, then revoke."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The dual-key grace window (5\u201310 minutes) prevents in-flight requests from failing during rotation; do not revoke the old key before propagation completes."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Maintain a break-glass procedure that revokes immediately and accepts brief outage \u2014 a compromised LLM key can cause thousands of dollars in charges within minutes."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Scan every commit for key patterns with gitleaks; subscribe to provider secret-scanning webhooks for defense-in-depth."
